 own travel arrangements after the end of the program. -Students with special diet requirements must bring 
 their necessary dietary supplements. -If I have any reason to leave the trip group, I must first obtain the 
 permission of a responsible SC staff member. This is for safety reasons.</p>
<p>5. If my conduct is deemed incompatible with the interests and the standards of the group and if my 
enrollment is TERMINATED, no refunds can be expected and returning to the United States is at my own expense. 
