on occasion, may include travel over long distances, on land, air and water, on safe transportation.</p>
<p>7. I grant SC permission to reproduce photographs or movies, of me taken during the period of time that 
I am participating in this program, including written statements I may make concerning this program.</p>
<p>8. The calendar deadline for all SC trip applications and all SC trip payments is eight (8) weeks before 
the beginning trip date for which you have applied. Our staff needs this to finalize reservations and 
services for you. When you submit an application, you will be placed on the ''applied for'' list for that trip. 
When you submit your payment you will be placed on the ''final trip list''.</p>
<p>9. I declare that I am not addicted or habituated to the use of non-/or prescription mood altering 
drugs/chemicals, including alcohol, and will not seek these drugs while on a SC trip.</p>
<p>10. A midnight curfew applies for the entire trip for safety reasons. This means that all trip participants 
and SC staff must be inside our hotel before midnight and remain there the rest of the night.</p>
<p>11. No alcohol abuse or any illicit drug use will be allowed. If this is violated, the participant(s) 
will be specifically warned, verbally and in writing, and a second violation can result in a dismissal of 
that participant from the remainder of the trip. There will be no refunds and any additional related 
expenses will be paid by that trip participant.</p>
<p>12. Travel and health insurance is the responsibility of each trip participant.</p>
<p>13. Any trip participant activities either before the in-country arrival day or after the end of the 
seventh day of the program are not the responsibility of SC. This includes any tours, visits or sightseeing 
that I may elect to do in the trip country or elsewhere. I do those things upon my own initiative and 
responsibility and at my own risk, whether before or after the SC trip.</p>
<ol>

<p>Please show this agreement to your parents or any other person(s) who may feel a shared responsibility for your well-being.</p>

<p>BE SURE TO MAKE YOUR OWN COPY OF THIS AGREEMENT FOR YOUR RECORDS</p>

<div class="from-group">
         <%= f.label :yes, "I have read and accept this agreement" %><br>
         <%= f.collection_check_boxes :yes, {}, {class:"checkbox-inline"} %>
      </div>
      <div class="col-xs-6 push-xs-3">
         <%= f.submit "GUARDAR", class: "btn btn-register btn-orange btn-block" %>
      </div>
      <% end %>
        <div class="clearfix"></div>
   </div>
</div>

		    </div>
            </div>